  "title": "The excellence of asking for Allah's blessings upon the Prophet PBUH",
  "source": "Hisn al-Muslim 222",
  "arabic": "وَقَالَ صلى الله عليه وسلم إِنَّ لِلَّهِ مَلاَئِكَةً سَيَّاحِينَ فِي الْأَرْضِ يُبَلِّغُونِي مِنْ أُمَّتِي السَّلاَمَ",
  "meaning": "The Prophet [PBUH] said:'Indeed Allah has angels who roam the earth and they convey to me the greetings (or prayers of peace) of my 'Ummah (nation).",
